steps.description:
This PR introduces a
```hcl
resource "time_rotating" "example" {
  rotation_days = 320
}

resource "grafana_cloud_access_policy_token" "this" {
  region           = "us"
  access_policy_id = grafana_cloud_access_policy.this.policy_id
  name             = "${local.cluster_name}-policy-token-${time_rotating.example.year}-${time_rotating.example.day}-${time_rotating.example.month}"
  display_name     = "${local.cluster_name} Policy Token"
  expires_at       = timeadd(time_rotating.example.rotation_rfc3339, "1080h") # add 45 days to the rotation time

  lifecycle {
    create_before_destroy = true
  }
}
```

